## ğŸ§© Overview

This repo provides hands-on examples of key vector-powered applications:

1. **Semantic Search** â€“ Retrieve relevant text using embeddings  
2. **RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)** â€“ Contextualize LLM output using vector retrieval  
3. **Anomaly Detection** â€“ Detect outliers via vector similarity  
4. **Hybrid Search** â€“ Combine semantic and metadata filtering  
5. **Image Similarity Search** â€“ Find visually similar images using embeddings  
6. **Recommender Systems** â€“ Recommend items based on embedding proximity  


---

## âš™ï¸ Tech Stack & Dependencies

- Python 3.8+
- [LangChain](https://github.com/langchain-ai/langchain)
- [Pinecone](https://www.pinecone.io)
- [Hugging Face Transformers](https://huggingface.co/docs/transformers)
- Optional: FAISS, Chroma, Qdrant, Weaviate, pgvector
- Streamlit / Plotly for visualization

